# [Ubuntu怎样安装Python3.6](https://www.cnblogs.com/yjlch1016/p/8641910.html)

Ubuntu默认安装了Python2.7和3.5

输入命令python

![](data:image/png;base64,)

按Ctrl+D退出python命令行

![](https://images2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1321829/201803/1321829-20180324215130873-705100820.png)

输入命令sudo add-apt-repository ppa:jonathonf/python-3.6

![](data:image/png;base64,)

按Enter确认

输入命令sudo apt-get update

输入命令sudo apt-get install python3.6

按Y确认



调整Python3的优先级，使得3.6优先级较高

sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python3 python3 /usr/bin/python3.5 1

sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python3 python3 /usr/bin/python3.6 2

更改默认值，python默认为Python2，现在修改为Python3

sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python2 100

sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python3 150



此时再输入命令python

![](https://images2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1321829/201803/1321829-20180324223743781-607955451.png)

可以看到已经是Python3.6了！

输入命令sudo apt-get install python-pip安装pip

输入命令sudo pip install --upgrade pip更新pip



添加Selenum模块

sudo -H pip install selenium

添加Appium模块

sudo -H pip install Appium-Python-Client
